    Automated:    trivy config <Dockerfile, helm charts, terraform>
                  Plus pytest tests/test_headers.py - verifies the
                  security headers are present on every response.
    Manual checklist:
      [ ] Debug mode OFF in any non-local environment - the app
          REFUSES to start with DEBUG=True bound to anything other
          than 127.0.0.1
      [ ] Default credentials changed (no admin/admin anywhere)
      [ ] Unused features and endpoints disabled
      [ ] Strict security headers: CSP, HSTS (preload-eligible),
          X-Frame-Options DENY, X-Content-Type-Options nosniff,
          Referrer-Policy strict-origin-when-cross-origin,
          Permissions-Policy restricting unused features
